岩岩發現條lan線係唔經modem"},{"pid":"90612237e617233af528bad7bf468c1929e5e0bb","tid":285131,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解你條lan 線個樣咁有趣？？？<br />\n<br />\n正常係牆身有條線入modem,之後modem 有條線插入router個wan,然後咪lan 1插條lan 線入去另一邊插去pc 囉</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知點解會咁<br />\n<br />\n但我岩岩發現條lan線係唔經modem</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n牆身應該有條光纖線直插modem,或者插住咗個盒仔，然後再有條線入modem,之後用另一條lan 線將modem,router同pc駁埋就ok"},{"pid":"f2a5c89b7a216a82aa42c287440f965ee886207c","tid":285131,"uid":34393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:53:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解你條lan 線個樣咁有趣？？？<br />\n<br />\n正常係牆身有條線入modem,之後modem 有條線插入router個wan,然後咪lan 1插條lan 線入去另一邊插去pc 囉</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知點解會咁<br />\n<br />\n但我岩岩發現條lan線係唔經modem</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n牆身應該有條光纖線直插modem,或者插住咗個盒仔，然後再有條線入modem,之後用另一條lan 線將modem,router同pc駁埋就ok</blockquote><br />\n搞掂左，唔該晒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來要setup完個router先可以係電腦上返網，仲以為只可以得一邊上網，真係玩死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b1106a4f2928077f55247d142e9c8c20efe583","tid":285131,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:43:23.000Z","msg":"？！<br />\n白綠白啡入，白橙白藍出？？？<br />\n玩乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d3df2cce149602984581e21b6a9878db69d40c","tid":285131,"uid":34393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>？！<br />\n白綠白啡入，白橙白藍出？？？<br />\n玩乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩色都好，搞掂左就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}